<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="not-only-but-also">not only ... but (also)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不但…而且：</strong></h4>
<p>注: not only … but (also) 可以连接并列成分。连接主语时，谓语与靠近它的主语一致。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not only the students but also their teacher is enjoying the film.
不仅学生们在欣赏这部影片，他们的老师也在欣赏。</p></div>

<p>注: not only … but (also) 连接两个并列分句时，not only所在的句子要用部分倒装语序。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not only can a beautiful smile make ourselves happy, but also it enables others to feel delighted.
一个灿烂的笑容不仅能使我们自己高兴，而且能使他人感到愉快。</p><footer>2010 湖北书面表达</footer></div></div>